# Generated / tool-owned output — not formatted by prettier.

# drizzle-kit owns these migration snapshots and SQL. Prettier and drizzle-kit
# disagree on JSON array wrapping, so checking them here would make the CI
# "Format" gate fight `pnpm db:generate` (the "Migration drift" gate) forever.
